      • getExtremeSpeed

        public static RunSetting getExtremeSpeed()
        ExtremeSpeed setting skips DataSet cleaning, organizing and RuleSet matrix production and definition production. It also sets all outputs types as CSV and State Analyzer 2.0 output type as TXT. Disables debugging.
        Returns:
        ExtremeSpeed RunSetting object.

      • getHighSpeed

        public static RunSetting getHighSpeed()
        HighSpeed setting enables all features but produces output in less professional way as CSV format. State Analyzer 2.0 output type is XLS. Disables debugging.
        Returns:
        HighSpeed RunSetting object.

      • getProfessionalSetting

        public static RunSetting getProfessionalSetting()
        ProfessionalSetting setting enables all features and produces output in a professional way as XLS format. State Analyzer 2.0 output type is XLS. Enables debugging.
        Returns:
        HighSpeed RunSetting object.
